Note: this following should be at the directory containing src, data.

0. To create symbolic link to the data:
		cd data
		ln -s /home/congyu/cs2580/hw2/instructor/data/wiki

1. To compile (first move to the parent directory after 0 is done): 
        javac -cp lib/jsoup-1.8.1.jar src/edu/nyu/cs/cs2580/*.java

2. To contruct index: 
        java -cp src:lib/jsoup-1.8.1.jar -Xmx512m edu.nyu.cs.cs2580.SearchEngine  --mode=index  --options=conf/engine.conf
3. To start server: 
        java -cp src:lib/jsoup-1.8.1.jar -Xmx512m edu.nyu.cs.cs2580.SearchEngine  --mode=serve --port=25813 --options=conf/engine.conf
To issue an query: 
        curl 'localhost:25813/search?query=grammy&ranker=conjunctive'
        curl 'localhost:25813/search?query=grammy+%22new+york%22&ranker=conjunctive'